/latest/20190215/1550217236502/【拍完《男朋友》】宋慧喬想與王家衛再合作\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190215%2F1550217236502%2F%E3%80%90%E6%8B%8D%E5%AE%8C%E3%80%8A%E7%94%B7%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E3%80%8B%E3%80%91%E5%AE%8B%E6%85%A7%E5%96%AC%E6%83%B3%E8%88%87%E7%8E%8B%E5%AE%B6%E8%A1%9B%E5%86%8D%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhN6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=860ee994\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190215%2F1550217236502%2F%E3%80%90%E6%8B%8D%E5%AE%8C%E3%80%8A%E7%94%B7%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E3%80%8B%E3%80%91%E5%AE%8B%E6%85%A7%E5%96%AC%E6%83%B3%E8%88%87%E7%8E%8B%E5%AE%B6%E8%A1%9B%E5%86%8D%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C&h=d336b6c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190215/1550217236502/【拍完《男朋友》】宋慧喬想與王家衛再合作</a><br />\n<br />\n早前拍完韓劇《男朋友》的宋慧喬，近日為韓國時尚雜誌《ELLE》拍攝最新一期雜誌封面。喬妹穿著春季新裝，展現「女神」魅力，造型清新優雅。<br />\n在雜誌訪問中，宋慧喬主動提到香港導演王家衛，「我想跟《一代宗師》王家衛導演再次合作，隨着時間流逝，以及年齡增長，我的外表也發生了變化，我很好奇再見導演時，自己又會是什麼樣子」。<br />\n<br />\n想嚟再拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:28:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">隨着時間流逝，以及年齡增長，我的外表也發生了變化</span><br />\n有乜變化都無用<br />\n拍五六年可能最後剪剩幾秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:31:07.000Z","msg":"你理得人 人哋鍾意想拍<br />\n幾秒又點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T00:32:33.000Z","msg":"春光乍洩關淑怡女主角剪到一秒都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dca048344c4804448c63a4182fbb403532ecfb0","tid":1104354,"uid":247521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T02:38:40.000Z","msg":"郭富城同發哥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪想玩鳩啲矮仔阿"},{"pid":"269a338655bcd4a98484c6974d448e093fffca94"